        "collapsible_item_eFemDY": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Product FAQ",
            "content": "<p>Welcome to Cedar Hospitality Suppliers, where we pride ourselves on providing exceptional service and high-quality products to our customers.<br/><br/>We are excited to be always launching new products that are fantastic additions to our world class range. The focus has, and always will be, to stock the largest range of the highest quality global and homegrown hospitality brands.<br/><br/>We are proud partners with global powerhouse brands like Steelite, Unox, Robot Coupe, BioPak, GI Metal and local brands such as Robert Gordon Pottery, Roband and LUUS.<br/><br/>All of our products are sent to you in good condition and are packaged correctly. We cannot guarantee the condition of the product on arrival. If you believe that there are any issues, problems or feel like your received product is not of quality such as being; broken, inaccurate, or damaged - please contact us atcedaronline@cedarhospitality.comor call us on 03 8388 6800 and we will attend to your query as soon as possible.<br/><br/></p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": true,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_RQ3WzW": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "When are you open?",
            "content": "<p>We are open Monday - Saturday. Our trading hours are:</p><p>Monday - Friday: 8:30AM - 5:30PM</p><p>Saturday - Sunday: 9:00AM - 4PM</p><p>You can visit us at our showroom on 223-231 Brunswick Rd, Brunswick, Victoria, 3056, Australia.</p><p>You can shop via our website 24/7.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_aKpRFm": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "I am not a business can I still buy for you?",
            "content": "<p>At Cedar, we don’t only serve business owners. There are several things in our selection that are suitable for usage at home. Our gorgeous china and glassware will wow your guests. Without high-performance tools and appliances, you can save time in the kitchen. You can visit our showroom and browse our extensive range of products and exclusive brands.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_3c4PkF": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "I’m not from Victoria, can I still order from your website?",
            "content": "<p>At Cedar, we ship Australia-wide. If you are a Metro Melbourne or CBD customer you can view our delivery calendar<a href=\"https://cedarhospitality.com/content/9-we-deliver\">here.</a>If you are not located in Australia, please contact our customer service staff by phone or email for additional information.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        }
