            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "What languages do you speak?",
            "content": "<p>Cedar is based in Melbourne, Australia, so English is our primary language. We also have staff members who speak Hindi, Chinese, Italian, Arabic, Croatian, Greek and French. Please let us know if you require linguistic assistance, and we will try our best to assist you in any way that we can.</p>",
