        "collapsible_item_aQb9Wh": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "What Industries do you service?",
            "content": "<p>At Cedar, we service all industries within the hospitality industry. Our website is divided into the following 5 primary hospitality sectors:</p><ul><li>Hotels, Events and Catering,</li><li>Healthcare,</li><li>Restaurants and Cafes,</li><li>Takeaways and Food Trucks</li><li>Bars and Cafes.</li></ul><p>We provide to any hospitality provider, whether that be</p><ul><li>Schools, TAFES and education sectors,</li><li>Wineries and Tourism centres,</li><li>Bakeries and confectionaries</li><li>Pizzerias and Fish and Chip Shops</li><li>Zoos and Aquariums</li><li>and many more.</li></ul><p>We are also open to the general public.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_LEFxHd": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Do you offer financial help or options?",
            "content": "<p>We accept a variety of payment methods, including Afterpay, PayPal, and Zip Pay. To ensure that you are adequately supported on your journey, SilverChef, Rent-Try-Buy and Easy-Own, have partnered with Cedar.<a href=\"https://cedarhospitality.com/silver-chef-finance/\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Click here </strong></em></a>for additional details.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "page": "",
            "open": false,
            "use_subtext_color": true
          }
        },
        "collapsible_item_L3reNd": {
          "type": "collapsible_item",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "What is your fulfilment process?",
            "content": "<p>At Cedar, we have our showroom located in Brunswick, Melbourne, which is home to our extensive range of brands and products. Also, we have our seamless online store that makes quick and simple delivery across the country possible.</p>",
